Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,100)}in this secret, little room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:40.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,100)}My memories embraced all mysteries and smashed them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,250)}with quiet prayers I overcame my suffering
