Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kakamigahara Guard Post?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure gotten older if you couldn't dodge that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Slicing Dragonfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Shinto weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it coming from the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's from deeper down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth's plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the Shin-Nagoya Platonic Plate Reactor?{weird name}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're starting a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll destroy all of Mikawa, not just Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's left in Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the automated dolls and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you discover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lord has only informed me that this is the beginning of the Genesis Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:58.83,spell,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs90\blur1.7\pos(1618.5,318)\c&HA38F7B&}{(brief flashback of the 10:33 typeset) - }Genesis Project
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Genesis Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it could potentially save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll bind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Slicing Dragonfly can sever things from existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Kakamigahara Guard Post burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I severed the guards' very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to fiddle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuno and I have to intercept those Testament Union bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron, they'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My display of loyalty is to protect my lord's wishes and prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So Tadatsugu, where does your loyalty stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So go, you no longer belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached a stop and shall begin turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluid output erupting from Shin-Nagoya Castle is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Detection levels have increased a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tres España's armed guard is taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A fleet of landing craft is approaching Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,K.P.A. Italia put our call on hold rather than blocking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Testament Union ships dispatched the Gods of War and commenced an assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd use anti-aerial mountain gear for putting out a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this was all just a feint...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Mikawa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This way the Testament Union can force their armament into Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Futayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you have us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather all officers on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Do as you like," eh, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wanted me to handle this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would Masazumi do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.19,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Deck Bow, Tama
